\par

\pard\f0\fs28 Leaves entire. Leaf-like bracts similar to the leaves but smaller, with a more or less reduced blade; spikes 3- to 6-flowered. Anthers extrorse, with a broad connective produced above the thecae into an appendage; pollen-grains filiform. Stigma sessile, irregularly lobed.
\par

